Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in a place like this you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone like you is more suited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go home, let's go to that karaoke place by the train station again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time Otani says or does something,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...I end up going to heaven, or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole world has been revolving around Otani, going round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:21.16,Title,,0,0,0,,Recapture Love!\NImprove as a Girl With Winning Chocolate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've been rejected once already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't got much confidence left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "Maybe Koizumi is crying again," or something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone like you is more suited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:58.20,Superscript,,0,0,0,,HOPE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he said a thing like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't help but hold out a bit of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the worst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go die, why don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to line up the edges before stapling them, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did line them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! How are these aligned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look. This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Why are you rambling like some old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not doing it properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be a stickler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're freaking irritating! Just shut up and work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they arguing about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I looks like they're organizing the print-outs for the next self study period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. And I lined them all up so neatly too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani's feelings are like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...a ramen stall owner standing behind a stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely shrouded in fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you come up with a better analogy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.62,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Self Study
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels like things are great right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Risa's ranking in the eyes of Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:09.04,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Koizumi Risa's ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as Kanzaki-san is concerned, you've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. From now on, just go for the finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Valentine's Day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him chocolates or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. In the end I didn't give him any chocolate last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If he says "Don't want it" again like last year, I'll never recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine to just let other girls give him chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He already knows I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run or hide or anything. I'd actually be giving him honmei chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of giving him obligatory chocolate now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be like confessing to him all over again. I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you don't want to? You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is rowdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get any Valentine's chocolate last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,F-F-From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, those girls that come and watch me play basketball all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just obligatory chocolate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment we had new members, they all flocked to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'll definitely get chocolate from at least one person this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna give me some, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. I want to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since you asked, I guess I could give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but you've given me a lot of presents lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll give you something in return next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll really get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be he's starting to have feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's asking me for chocolate, does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-senpai! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka! Seiko-chan! What are you guys up to? Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Home Ec Club going to make chocolate for Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're picking up some supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-senpai, why don't you make chocolate with us and give it to Otani-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all make something together, it'll save money, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, that's true. Well then....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're giving chocolate to that midget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll give you some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That attitude... It's like you don't care about me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be getting chocolate from your girlfriends anyway, right, Haruka-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,By dating various different types of women, I'll grow as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for the sake of one day going out with you, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out with them one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much life left in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe ninety years left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-senpai, how are things going with Otani-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all lovely-dovey now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Haven't I told you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You got rejected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?! Why did he reject you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, he can't see me as his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about it. I don't want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,LIKE HELL!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn midget... I'll cram him into a vacuum cleaner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. You were rejected, but you're still giving him chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say "You were rejected."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You were rejected. Well, whatever. Why are you still giving him chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You still love him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chan, you truly understand this lonely maiden's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! I'm a maiden too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Seishirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Seiko! I'm a maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to understand that kind of maiden's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Risa, just forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget all about that idiot who rejected you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I think he'll fall for me eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it feels like things are going well at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.00,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best! I'll be cheering for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him... That damn midget...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It doesn't matter if it takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just slowly, slowly become captivated by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross. what's got you in such a good mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A new album will be out in Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For real? We've gotta get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be doing another concert too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Who else would I go to an Umibouzu concert with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to book tickets soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that, you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukagawa Haruka. Handsome seventeen year old boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Risa's childhood frien—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Haruka, what were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You rejected Risa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The comedy duo is breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this more material?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Tell me exactly what you think is wrong with Risa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean... that's... how should I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Why do I have to explain myself to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you had the nerve to do that, stay away from Risa, from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop toying with her maiden heart, you playboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're being cruel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then what is it lik-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww, oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You really rejected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you seemed to get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on Risa's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on Nobu-chan's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Don't do pointless stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that guy is so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He rejected you, but he's still going around smiling like nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to how dense a person can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I told him to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him to not worry about it and just act the way he did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's fine, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop interfering or I'll bite your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's fine. I'll work hard on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So just leave me alone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, Otani. How could you reject such a nice girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel... You're so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute, you guys. At least hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, don't worry about what Haruka did just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray for Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, everyone's cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what's going on, but I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really a playboy who's toying with a maiden's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you feel about Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"How"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're asking me whether I like or dislike her, I'd say I like her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want her to be your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, suppose she was my girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd have to kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's kind of comical?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're laughing, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. I'm breaking out in a cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought it'd only be a matter of time before you guys would go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you talk to her, you seem like you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like after that incident with Kanzaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it from Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "Maybe Koizumi is crying again," or something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone like you is more suited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just saying what was on my mind without really thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't you ask her for Valentine's chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to eat chocolate. There's no meaning behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You natural flirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not, you idiot! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A casual comment from you makes Koizumi-san more flustered than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't make it sound so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we made too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if darling is finished with his club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a day early, but I'm going to give these to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, do you want to bring yours over too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. I've prepared the wrapping and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really giving that to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, would you? Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get any. Eat what you made yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said you were gonna give me some...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really going to give that midget chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so short...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally lacking in nutrition...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good. I'm too nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to the washroom for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Haruka, I'm even more determined now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run or hide any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely honmei chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept my feelings, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? This feeling...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This... isn't obligatory chocolate, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... couldn't you just make it obligatory chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean? You won't accept it if it's honmei chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wanted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, you can't accept my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, the teacher's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop by the office, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Did I interrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Risa. Darling said some pointless things to Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you aren't interested, don't be so nice to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say something cool like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... even if he's not interested, I'll be happy if he's still nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll try even harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a real idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept honmei chocolate when my own feelings are still uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so extreme! Are you trying to be a tough guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you were so dense, or a playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done anything wrong, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone is in the wrong it's me, for refusing to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't care if you like or hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say whatever is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just take it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that it's honmei chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if it takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he gradually starts to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But the girl who's fallen for me is a real idiot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to say whatever I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you trying to piss me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.77,Superscript,,0,0,0,,IDIOT MIDGET
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't let that idiot get Risa's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does St. Valentine just hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, what are you doing at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! All alone with Otani-kun in his room huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the least bit tempted to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Heating up! A First Kiss in His Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
